body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Jonathan Barnes and I'm a customer service representative at XYZ Auto, how may I assist you today? May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Brittany. Could you please confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's the twenty-first of July, one nine eight eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Brittany. And could you also provide me with the last four digits of your phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's six five four three.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Brittany. Is there anything specific you would like assistance with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling frustrated about the pricing at your dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern, Brittany. Let's work together to resolve this issue. Thank you for your time and patience.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Have a great day and goodbye.
